    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/c541498c7f77c0efc222b9e440d6a4e4.poster.avif?t=1747084607\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/c541498c7f77c0efc222b9e440d6a4e4.webm?t=1747084607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/c541498c7f77c0efc222b9e440d6a4e4.mp4?t=1747084607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/a766c2d6595ced1593186c8cc5644412.avif?t=1747084607\" width=640 height=93 /></span><br>神秘组织被人遗忘千百年，如今重现世间，成员自称披萨特工！<br> <br>披萨特工权限高于政府人员，配备生物可降解装备，普通安检无法发现，身份完全不为外界所知，因而可以置敌于死地，而且不论什么情况，都能自由行动，不受其他国家法规约束。<br> <br>他们的使命是什么？消除美食祸患，维护世界平衡……<br> <br>秘密特工艾斯·楚什将被迫相应征召，开展一次非常惊险的行动——阻止“艾尔·柯西内罗”的图谋。“艾尔·柯西内罗”是某个犯罪酱汁主厨的代号，此人在世界各地策划一系列烹饪袭击，企图借此成为空前绝后的天下第一大厨……<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/e3a64dbd314e47096e33d1d24ffe64f5.avif?t=1747084607\" width=640 height=93 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/a2febb49267fd3c08c7d75074d0e7b0b.webp?t=1747084607\" width=30 height=18 /></span>  黑色喜剧冒险游戏《Detective Gallo》（《公鸡神探》）开发团队奉上全新动作喜剧冒险游戏，让你化身秘密特工艾斯·楚什，以幽默夸张的方式体验间谍题材游戏！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318870/extras/a2febb49267fd3c08c7d75074d0e7b0b.webp?t=1747084607\" width=30 height=18 /></span>  隐秘模式（潜行）还是公开模式（直接行动）？你来决定。相同的难题，不同的解决方法，按照你的喜好完成游戏特定的片段！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video cl